title: Webinar: Dev Superpowers - Bootstrap
eventShortDescription: ​Bootstrap is a sleek, intuitive, and powerful mobile first front-end framework for faster and easier web development. Join Ben as he shows you how easy it is to make use of the framework, and step beyond the "just another bootstrap site" look and feel.
